{"tid":1387831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好似未意識到要團結到點既地步先會贏","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:55.000Z","uid":201178,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"552861650126c6d10be254834f645a8c1a578979","tid":1387831,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"就係你身邊既每一個人都支持呢場運動，<br />\n講緊既係你坐地鐵隔離個位，<br />\n買麥當勞排你前面個位，<br />\n屋企食飯炒菜個位。<br />\n<br />\n點解前線宜家每一步都咁辛苦，講到尾就係<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔夠人，唔夠錢，唔夠支持<br />\n</span><br />\n可能你覺得我好撚左膠，唔緊要，<br />\n但想像下如果各自既身邊人都比自己感染到，<br />\n好快，我地每一步都冇咁辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">裝睡的人打得醒。<br />\n宜家個社會已經直接威脅人身安全，<br />\n只要我地每人加多兩句，<br />\n咩色都會慢慢邁向光明的黃。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，唔好再講咩無用，宜家就係和理非既天下，<br />\n用盡你一切既方法，傳播你相信既信念。<br />\n請相信<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">念念不忘，必有迴響。<br />\n香港人加油。<br />\n</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"38a2dd3183db9d8aacf67c056147b298c15c4041","tid":1387831,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e084a3a60bd9f3b334aa0e2aca1b452c31ae57d7","tid":1387831,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"31b00910e1f593b20e8ca376445d2bb00356a2cb","tid":1387831,"uid":28223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aa23c1e3b4ca0d6b11640bcc79eee973fcb709","tid":1387831,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},{"pid":"8e193ba64a0747c8d9ce34430a2ae20cd38da57c","tid":1387831,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"40701db49653